title: The Real Housewives Of New Jersey S06E16 Reunion Part 1 WEB-DL x
description:
Ep 16: Reunion Part 1
Dina opens up about where she stands with Caroline, Jacqueline, and the rest of her family.
PREMIERE: Nov 2, 2014, 9:00 PM

The ladies of the Garden State reunite with host Andy Cohen to discuss everything that went down in Season 6. In true Jersey fashion, family plays a big part as Rosie and Kathy join the Housewives, and a conversation leads Teresa Giudice to leave the couch. After years of silence, Dina opens up about where she stands with Caroline, Jacqueline, and the rest of her family, and whether or not she sees a mend in the future
